reviews.text: Great all day full English breakfasts. Big portions for around 50 to 70 HKD. Coffee is not very generous and could do with more beans but overall a good filling way to start the day. One of the better western style breakfast options at Double Cove. Opens at 9am and gets busy quickly.
Food is ok, but staff can do a bit more smile.

Tasty, lots of options there. Rice, noodles and those all day breakfast sets are great! By the way, those All day breakfast sets are huge, probably could feed 2 children. 😅 And they're not expensive too in this area. Recommended!

Nice, casual, light atmosphere. The food is good (not fine dining level), though it is a little pricey. The portion sizes are way too large - one portion could feed three people.

Note that they only accept cash - no card or Octopus.
All day breakfast was good

reviews.text: Quiet place with some restaurants and a supermarket.  Locate near Lake Silver and Wu Kai Sha station.   Air is good and near sea.

Very quiet and pleasant environment. Uses natural lighting which feels quite nice. The modern design of the shopping mall plus the extraordinary WiFi makes it a great place. However, since it uses natural lighting, this place can get a bit stuffy on the top floor. There is not much variety of choices, as most shops are either restaurants or convenience
 stores.
All you would find here is restaurants after restaurants after restaurants. Plenty of food choices, but food quality's meh.
Nice, small and quiet shopping centre, not much to buy.  Clean and not many people, mainly residents.  Next to Lake Silver.  Lots of people bring their dogs around.  Lovely place
Romantic lighting at night. What a new era shopping mall for all age

reviews.text:
French toast all day breakfast $65🙆🏻‍♀️
厚厚的西多士炸得金黃，
伴牛油蜜糖吃，份量夠實在！
還有脆脆的薯餅，
煎得油香撲鼻的香腸，
輕輕一點沙拉🥗粟米減一減罪惡感😂

好邪惡但好滿足的午餐！

雖然距離有點遠，但駕車去還算方便的！
商場的停車場🅿️一般不會很滿，
泊車優惠的門檻也不高，
2.3個人吃個午餐就夠了！

Great all day full English breakfasts. Big portions for around 50 to 70 HKD. Coffee is not very generous and could do with more beans but overall a good filling way to start the day. One of the better western style breakfast options at Double Cove. Opens at 9am and gets busy quickly.
食物質素比第一城果間好好多，等位亦快

食物新鮮，即叫即做，珈琲好味，但切記衹收現錢，
